sentence: what rivers do not run through tennessee ?
sentence-with-vars: what rivers do not run through state0 ?
sql: select river.river_name from river where river.river_name not in ( select river.river_name from river where river.traverse = ' tennessee ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select river.river_name from river where river.river_name not in ( select river.river_name from river where river.traverse = ' state0 ' ) ;
